[
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">Listen</st> to the <st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\"><span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span>\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st>, you <st data-num=\"01121 03478\">Israelites</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has a <st data-num=\"07379\" class=\"\">covenant lawsuit</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">against</st> the <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">people</st> of <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">Israel</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">there is neither</st> <st data-num=\"0571\" class=\"\">faithfulness</st> <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">nor</st> <st data-num=\"02617\" class=\"\">loyalty</st> in the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>, <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">nor</st> do they <st data-num=\"01847\" class=\"\">acknowledge</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">There is only <st data-num=\"0422\" class=\"\">cursing</st>, <st data-num=\"03584\" class=\"\">lying</st>, <st data-num=\"07523\" class=\"\">murder</st>, <st data-num=\"01589\" class=\"\">stealing</st>, and <st data-num=\"05003\" class=\"\">adultery</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"06555\" class=\"\">resort to violence</st> and <st data-num=\"01818 01818 05060\">bloodshed</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921 03651\">Therefore</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> will <st data-num=\"056\" class=\"\">mourn</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> its <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">inhabitants</st> will <st data-num=\"0535\" class=\"\">perish</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"07704\" class=\"\">wild</st> <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">animals</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"05775\" class=\"\">birds</st> of the <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">sky</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">even</st> the <st data-num=\"01709\" class=\"\">fish</st> in the <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">sea</st> will <st data-num=\"0622\" class=\"\">perish</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> let <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">anyone</st> <st data-num=\"07378\" class=\"\">accuse</st> <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"03198\" class=\"\">contend</st> against <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">anyone</st> else,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">for my <st data-num=\"07378\" class=\"\">case</st> is <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">against</st> you <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">You <st data-num=\"03782\" class=\"\">stumble</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> and <st data-num=\"03915\" class=\"\">night</st>, <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">and</st> the false <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophets</st> <st data-num=\"03782\" class=\"\">stumble</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> you;<p class=\"poetry\">you have <st data-num=\"01820\" class=\"\">destroyed</st> your own <st data-num=\"0517\" class=\"\">people</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">You have <st data-num=\"01820\" class=\"\">destroyed</st><n id=\"1\" /> my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <p class=\"poetry\">by <st data-num=\"01097\" class=\"\">failing</st> to <st data-num=\"01847\" class=\"\">acknowledge</st> me! <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Because</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> <st data-num=\"03988\" class=\"\">refuse</st> to <st data-num=\"01847\" class=\"\">acknowledge</st> me,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"03988\" class=\"\">reject</st> you as my <st data-num=\"03547\" class=\"\">priests</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Because you <st data-num=\"07911\" class=\"\">reject</st><n id=\"3\" /> the <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st> of your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01571 0589\">I</st> will <st data-num=\"07911\" class=\"\">reject</st><n id=\"4\" /> your <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">descendants</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The more the priests <st data-num=\"07235\" class=\"\">increased in numbers</st>, <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">the more</st> they <st data-num=\"02398\" class=\"\">rebelled</st> against me.<p class=\"poetry\">They have <st data-num=\"04171\" class=\"\">turned</st><n id=\"1\" /> their <st data-num=\"03519\" class=\"\">glorious calling</st> <p class=\"poetry\">into a <st data-num=\"07036\" class=\"\">shameful disgrace</st>! </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">feed on</st> the <st data-num=\"02403\" class=\"\">sin offerings</st> of my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">their <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">appetites</st> <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">long</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">for</st> their <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">iniquity</st>! </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">deal with</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> and <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> together:<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"06485 05921\">punish</st> them both for their <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">ways</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">and I will <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">repay</st> them for their <st data-num=\"04611\" class=\"\">deeds</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">eat</st>, but <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07646\" class=\"\">be satisfied</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">they will <st data-num=\"02181\" class=\"\">engage in prostitution</st>, but <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06555\" class=\"\">increase in numbers</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> they have <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">abandoned</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span><p class=\"poetry\">by <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">pursuing</st> <st data-num=\"02184\" class=\"\">other gods</st>.<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03196\" class=\"\">Old</st> and <st data-num=\"08492\" class=\"\">new</st> <st data-num=\"03196 08492\">wine</st> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">take away</st> the <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">understanding</st> of my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>.<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"07592\" class=\"\">consult</st> their <st data-num=\"06086\" class=\"\">wooden idols</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">and their <st data-num=\"04731\" class=\"\">diviner\u2019s staff</st> <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">answers with an oracle</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">wind</st> of <st data-num=\"02183\" class=\"\">prostitution</st> <st data-num=\"08582\" class=\"\">blows</st> them <st data-num=\"08582\" class=\"\">astray</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"02181\" class=\"\">commit spiritual adultery</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"08478\" class=\"\">against</st> their <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"02076\" class=\"\">sacrifice</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"07218 02022\">mountaintops</st> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"06999\" class=\"\">burn offerings</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"01389\" class=\"\">hills</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">they sacrifice<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"08478\" class=\"\">under</st> <st data-num=\"0437\" class=\"\">oak</st>, <st data-num=\"03839\" class=\"\">poplar</st>, and <st data-num=\"0424\" class=\"\">terebinth</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> their <st data-num=\"06738\" class=\"\">shade</st> is so <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">pleasant</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921 03651\">As a result</st>, your <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">daughters</st> have <st data-num=\"02181\" class=\"\">become cult prostitutes</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and your <st data-num=\"03618\" class=\"\">daughters-in-law</st> <st data-num=\"05003\" class=\"\">commit adultery</st>! </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06485 05921\">punish</st> your <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">daughters</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">when</st> they <st data-num=\"02181\" class=\"\">commit prostitution</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">nor your <st data-num=\"03618\" class=\"\">daughters-in-law</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">when</st> they <st data-num=\"05003\" class=\"\">commit adultery</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">men</st> <st data-num=\"06504\" class=\"\">consort</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> <st data-num=\"02181\" class=\"\">harlots</st>; <p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"02076\" class=\"\">sacrifice</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> <st data-num=\"06948\" class=\"\">temple prostitutes</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">It is true:<n id=\"1\" /> \u201cA <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> that <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">lacks</st> <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">understanding</st> will <st data-num=\"03832\" class=\"\">come to ruin</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Although</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st>, O <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, <st data-num=\"02181\" class=\"\">commit adultery</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> let <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> <st data-num=\"0816\" class=\"\">become guilty</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">journey</st> to <st data-num=\"01537\" class=\"\">Gilgal</st>. <p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">go up</st> to <st data-num=\"01007\" class=\"\">Beth Aven</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07650\" class=\"\">swear</st>, \u201cAs surely as the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">lives</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> has <st data-num=\"05637\" class=\"\">rebelled</st><n id=\"1\" /> like a <st data-num=\"05637\" class=\"\">stubborn</st> <st data-num=\"06510\" class=\"\">heifer</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">Soon</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> will <st data-num=\"07462\" class=\"\">put</st> them <st data-num=\"07462\" class=\"\">out to pasture</st><p class=\"poetry\">like a <st data-num=\"03532\" class=\"\">lamb</st> in a <st data-num=\"04800\" class=\"\">broad field</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0669\" class=\"\">Ephraim</st> has <st data-num=\"02266\" class=\"\">attached</st> himself <st data-num=\"02266\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"06091\" class=\"\">idols</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"03240\" class=\"\">not go near</st> him!</p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">consume</st> their <st data-num=\"05435\" class=\"\">alcohol</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">then <st data-num=\"02181\" class=\"\">engage</st> in <st data-num=\"02181\" class=\"\">cult prostitution</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"0157\" class=\"\">dearly</st> <st data-num=\"0157\" class=\"\">love</st> <st data-num=\"04043\" class=\"\">their</st> <st data-num=\"07036\" class=\"\">shameful behavior</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Hosea",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">A <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">whirlwind</st> has <st data-num=\"06887\" class=\"\">wrapped</st> them in its <st data-num=\"03671\" class=\"\">wings</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">they will be <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">brought to shame</st> because of their <st data-num=\"02077\" class=\"\">idolatrous worship</st>.<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "19"
  }
]